699
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:02,460
No labels.

700
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:04,620
Let's just look at the facts, alright?

701
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:07,140
Shen Minghui has been
in high school for five years.

702
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:08,180
Is that a fact?

703
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:11,020
All Shen Minghui thinks about

704
00:31:11,020 --> 00:31:12,140
is business and making money.

705
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:13,500
He doesn't focus on his studies.

706
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,620
Is that a fact?

707
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:16,780
Just think about it.

708
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:19,420
You've studied hard for years.

709
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:20,900
You're this close to making it.

710
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:22,780
Sir, I will focus on my studies.

711
00:31:23,060 --> 00:31:23,660
This won't do.

712
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:25,380
Have your father

713
00:31:25,620 --> 00:31:26,620
come to school tomorrow.

714
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:36,260
Lu Bing.

715
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:40,380
Your father doesn't
have to come tomorrow,

716
00:31:40,860 --> 00:31:42,900
but you must promise me one thing.

717
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:45,620
Before the college entrance exam,

718
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:47,740
you stay far, far away
from that Shen Minghui.

719
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:48,660
Can you do it?

720
00:31:54,300 --> 00:31:54,980
Shen Minghui.

721
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:56,940
Mr. Sun.

722
00:31:58,420 --> 00:32:00,100
Why are you bouncing ball?

723
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:02,220
We have PE next period.

724
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:02,780
Stop!

725
00:32:04,140 --> 00:32:05,950
I'm warming up for PE.
What's wrong with that?

726
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:06,740
You're not having PE anymore.

727
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,940
The PE teacher is out sick.

728
00:32:08,100 --> 00:32:09,220
Next period is math.

729
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:18,220
Listen, Shen Minghui,

730
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:19,980
if you don't feel like studying,

731
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,240
but don't drag other people down.

732
00:32:21,250 --> 00:32:22,420
If you don't want to be here,

733
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:24,270
say the word,
I'll approve your leave anytime.

734
00:32:24,700 --> 00:32:25,340
I'll study.

735
00:32:25,740 --> 00:32:26,660
Go back inside then!

736
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:35,420
Lu Bing,

737
00:32:35,940 --> 00:32:37,740
remember your promise.

738
00:32:40,980 --> 00:32:41,700
Go in.

739
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:53,540
What? You want to complain

740
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:54,780
(Principal's Office)
Mr. Sun for taking PE's time?

741
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:56,740
(Strive on, stay humble.)
In short,

742
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,950
it all comes down to one thing,

743
00:32:58,380 --> 00:32:59,180
teachers,

744
00:32:59,780 --> 00:33:01,700
the college entrance
exam is getting closer.

745
00:33:02,260 --> 00:33:04,660
I hope everyone gives it their all

746
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,860
to get every student

747
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,380
into their best possible shape.

748
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:11,500
(Dad)

749
00:33:12,660 --> 00:33:13,420
Mr. Hu Gang,

750
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:17,050
as a representative of the younger
faculty, please say a few words.

751
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:24,940
I can't speak for anyone else,

752
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:27,780
I can only speak for myself.

753
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,220
Our current senior year students

754
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:31,980
have very uneven grades,

755
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:34,900
but I think physics
is actually a subject

756
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:36,900
that can bring their scores up now.

757
00:33:37,220 --> 00:33:39,820
So I'm willing to shoulder more,

758
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:40,920
give myself extra pressure.

759
00:33:40,980 --> 00:33:42,500
Whatever others don't want to do,

760
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:43,740
I'll take it on.

761
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:44,940
Okay.

762
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:47,660
Since Mr. Hu Gang

763
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:48,780
has volunteered,

764
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:50,340
he will step up to the task.

765
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,300
Here's the thing,

766
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:53,980
due to

767
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:55,380
certain circumstances,

768
00:33:55,740 --> 00:33:56,960
Mr. Sun can no longer

769
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:58,890
continue as homeroom teacher
of Class 2 Senior 3.

770
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:01,260
Please take over then, Mr. Hu.

771
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:03,500
Me?

772
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:05,500
You got this.

773
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:11,380
Okay, Mr. Pan.

774
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:13,740
Class,

775
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:16,840
the college entrance exam
is just around the corner.

776
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:18,500
As

777
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:22,740
the final homeroom
teacher for Class 2 Senior 3,

778
00:34:23,340 --> 00:34:24,740
I'm under a lot of pressure.

779
00:34:24,740 --> 00:34:25,860
(Test Point 1:
Static Equilibrium Problems)

780
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,460
But

781
00:34:26,900 --> 00:34:28,900
from a physics perspective,

782
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:32,820
