783
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,900
Think about a steam engine,

784
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:37,380
only when enough pressure builds up

785
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:39,700
does it produce kinetic energy.

786
00:34:40,140 --> 00:34:42,460
So starting today,

787
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:46,940
I want us to push forward together

788
00:34:47,420 --> 00:34:48,780
and fight for every one of you

789
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,180
to get into the university
you're aiming for.

790
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,690
Next,

791
00:34:59,310 --> 00:35:01,980
for the ten students who ranked
at the bottom in last month's exam,

792
00:35:02,660 --> 00:35:05,980
I'll be meeting your parents one by one.

793
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:07,300
But don't panic,

794
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,100
it's not to complain.

795
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:11,940
I'm hoping that we, the teachers,

796
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:14,100
students, and parents,

797
00:35:14,500 --> 00:35:15,860
can join forces,

798
00:35:15,860 --> 00:35:16,980
unite our efforts,

799
00:35:17,700 --> 00:35:20,500
and make one final push together.

800
00:35:21,380 --> 00:35:21,980
Mr. Hu.

801
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:24,460
Yes?

802
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:26,940
