00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:06,340
Hey, dad.

823
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:07,380
Hi, Ni.

824
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,020
I heard you're going to the school

825
00:36:09,020 --> 00:36:10,380
to play stand-in dad for Minghui?

826
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:12,160
Just filling in for today.

827
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:14,620
Get his homeroom teacher's
contact for me.

828
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:15,260
Why?

829
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:18,940
Be nice to him.

830
00:36:18,940 --> 00:36:20,800
Who knows, he might
be your future son-in-law.

831
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:23,940
Got it!

832
00:36:24,470 --> 00:36:25,900
The scores can improve very quickly.

833
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:30,740
So, Mr. Shen,

