take whatever punishment comes.

939
00:40:32,540 --> 00:40:33,380
Get back here.

940
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,550
If anyone's going to beat you,
it'll be your own mother.

941
00:40:42,420 --> 00:40:43,580
My mom knows

